@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = REPLACE_WITH_VALID_JWT
@eventId = 000000000000000000000000
@bookingId = 000000000000000000000000

### Crea una prenotazione per l'evento indicato
POST {{baseUrl}}/events/{{eventId}}/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "seats": 1,
  "note": "Prenotazione di test"
}

### Elenca le prenotazioni dell'evento (includendo il conteggio posti disponibili)
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/{{eventId}}/bookings?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Aggiorna i posti prenotati
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/bookings/{{bookingId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "seats": 2,
  "status": "CONFIRMED"
}

### Cancella una prenotazione esistente
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings/{{bookingId}}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
